quran[31]{c,v,t}:
  38,21,"whl ja'ak -ayha alrswl- khabar almtkhasimayn alldhayn tswwara ealaa dawud fi makan ebadth, fartae min dkhwlhma elyh? qaluu lh: la takhaf, fnhn khasman zalam 'ahadana alakhr, faqd baynana baledl, wala tajur ealayna fi alhkm, warshidna 'iilaa swa' alsbyl"
  38,22,"whl ja'ak -ayha alrswl- khabar almtkhasimayn alldhayn tswwara ealaa dawud fi makan ebadth, fartae min dkhwlhma elyh? qaluu lh: la takhaf, fnhn khasman zalam 'ahadana alakhr, faqd baynana baledl, wala tajur ealayna fi alhkm, warshidna 'iilaa swa' alsbyl"
  38,23,"qal ahdhma: 'iina hdha 'akhi lah tise watiseun min alneaj, walays eindi 'iilaa naejatan wahdt, ftme fyha, wqal: aetnyha, wghlbny bhjth"
  38,24,"qal dawd: laqad zalamak 'akhuk bswalh dama naejatik 'iilaa neajh, wa'iina kthyrana min alshuraka' lyetdy bedhm ealaa bed, wyzlmh bakhdh haqah wedm 'insafh min nafsih 'iilaa almuminin alsalhyn, fala ybghy bedhm ealaa bed, wahum qlyl. wayqn dawud 'anana ftnnah bhdhh alkhswmt, fastaghfar rbh, wsjd tqrbana llh, warajae 'iilayh wtab"
  38,25,"fghfrna lah dhlk, wajaealnah min almqrrabyn endna, waeddna lah hasan almasir fi alakhrt"
  38,26,"ya dawud 'iinaa astkhlfnak fi al'ard wmllaknak fyha, fahkum bayn alnaas bialeadl wal'insaf, wala tatabie alhwa fi alahkam, fyudlk dhlk ean din allah wshreh, 'iina aladhin yadillun ean sabil allah lahum eadhab 'alim fi alnar; bghflthm ean yawm aljaza' walhsab. wafi hdha tawsiat lwlat al'amr 'ana yhkmu bialhaqi almanzil min allh, tabarak wteala, wala yedlu enh, fydlu ean sbylh"
  38,27,"wama khalaqna alsama' wal'ard wama baynahuma ebthana wlhwana, dhlk znn aladhin kfru, fawayl lahum min alnaar yawm alqyamt; lznhm albatl, wakufrihim ballh"
  38,28,"anjel aladhin amanuu waeamiluu alsaalihat kalmufsidin fi alard, 'am najeal 'ahl altqwa almuminin kashab alfjwr alkafryn? hadhih altaswiat ghyr layqt bhkmt allah whukmh, fala yastawun eind allh, bal ythyb allah almuminin alatqya', wyeaqb almufsidin alashqya'"
  38,29,"hdha almwha bih 'iilayk -ayha alrswl- kitab 'anzalnah 'iilayk mbark; lytfkru fi ayath, wyemlu bhdayath wdlalath, waliatadhakar 'ashab aleqwl alsalimat ma klfhm allah bh"
  38,30,"wwhbna ldawd aibnih slyman, fanemna bih elyh, waqrrna bih eynh, niem aleabd slyman, 'iinah kan kthyr alrujue 'iilaa allah wal'inabt 'ilyh"
  38,31,"adhkr hin euridt ealayh esrana alkhywl al'asilat alsryet, taqif ealaa thlath qwaym wtrfe alrabet; lnjabtha wkhftha, fama zalat tuerd ealayh hataa ghabat alshms"
  38,32,"fqal: 'iinani atharat hubi almal ean dhikr rabiy hataa ghabat alshams ean eynyh, ruddu ely alkhayl alty eurdt min qbl, fshre ymsh swqha waenaqha"
  38,33,"fqal: 'iinani atharat hubi almal ean dhikr rabiy hataa ghabat alshams ean eynyh, ruddu ely alkhayl alty eurdt min qbl, fshre ymsh swqha waenaqha"
  38,34,"wlqd abtlyna sulayman wa'alqayna ealaa kursiuh shiqun walad, wulid lah hin 'uqsim lytwfnn ealaa nsayh, wklhn tati bfars yujahid fi sabil allh, walam yql: 'in sha' allh, fataf ealayhina jmyeana, falam tahmil minhuna 'iilaa aimra'at wahidat ja'at bishiqi wld, thuma raje sulayman 'iilaa rabih wtab, qal: rabi aghfir li dhnby, waetny mlkana ezymana khasana la yakun mithlih li'ahad min albashar bedy, 'ink- sbhank- kthyr aljwd waleta'. fastajabna lh, wdhllna alriyh tajri bi'amrih tyiet mae quatuha wshdtha hayth arad"
  38,35,"walaqad abtlyna sulayman wa'alqayna ealaa kursiuh shiqun walad, wulid lah hin 'uqsim lytwfnn ealaa nsayh, wklhn tati bfars yujahid fi sabil allh, walam yql: 'in sha' allh, fataf ealayhina jmyeana, falam tahmil minhuna 'iilaa aimra'at wahidat ja'at bishiqi wld, thuma raje sulayman 'iilaa rabih wtab, qal: rabi aghfir li dhnby, waetny mlkana ezymana khasana la yakun mithlih li'ahad min albashar bedy, 'ink- sbhank- kthyr aljwd waleta'. fastajabna lh, wdhllna alriyh tajri bi'amrih tyiet mae quatuha wshdtha hayth arad"
  38,36,"wlqd abtlyna sulayman wa'alqayna ealaa kursiuh shiqun walad, wulid lah hin 'uqsim lytwfnn ealaa nsayh, wklhn tati bfars yujahid fi sabil allh, walam yql: 'in sha' allh, fataf ealayhina jmyeana, falam tahmil minhuna 'iilaa aimra'at wahidat ja'at bishiqi wld, thuma raje sulayman 'iilaa rabih wtab, qal: rabi aghfir li dhnby, waetny mlkana ezymana khasana la yakun mithlih li'ahad min albashar bedy, 'ink- sbhank- kthyr aljwd waleta'. fastajabna lh, wdhllna alriyh tajri bi'amrih tyiet mae quatuha wshdtha hayth arad"
  38,37,"wskhkharna lah alshayatin ystemlhm fi aemalh: faminhum albnawwn walghwwaswn fi albhar, wakhrwn, wahum mrdt alshyatyn, mwthwqwn fi alaghlal. hdha almulk aleazim waltskhyr alkhasi eatawuna lak ya slyman, faet man shit wamne man shyt, la hisab elyk"
  38,38,"wskhkharna lah alshayatin ystemlhm fi aemalh: faminhum albnawwn walghwwaswn fi albhar, wakhrwn, wahum mrdt alshyatyn, mwthwqwn fi alaghlal. hdha almulk aleazim waltskhyr alkhasi eatawuna lak ya slyman, faet man shit wamne man shyt, la hisab elyk"
  38,39,"wskhkharna lah alshayatin ystemlhm fi aemalh: faminhum albnawwn walghwwaswn fi albhar, wakhrwn, wahum mrdt alshyatyn, mwthwqwn fi alaghlal. hdha almulk aleazim waltskhyr alkhasi eatawuna lak ya slyman, faet man shit wamne man shyt, la hisab elyk"
  38,40,w'in lisulayman eindana fi aldaar alakhirat laqrbtan wahusn mrje
  38,41,"wadhkr -ayha alrswl- eabdana aywb, hin daea rabah 'ana alshaytan tasabab li bteb wmshqt, walm fi jsdy wmaly wahly"
  38,42,"fqlna lh: adrib birijlik al'ard ynbe lak minha ma'an bard, fashrb mnh, waghtsil fayadhhab eank alduru waladha"
  38,43,"fkshfna eanh durah wakrmnah wawahabna lah 'ahlah min zawjat wwld, wzdnah mathaluhum binin whfdt, kl dhlk rahmatan mnna bih w'ikramana lah ealaa sbrh, webrt wdhkra li'ashab aleqwl alslymt; liaelamuu 'ana eaqibat alsabr alfrj wakashf aldr"
  38,44,"wqlna lh: khudh biadik huzmt shmarykh, fadrib biha zawjak 'ibrarana bymynk, fala thnth; 'iidh 'uqsim lydrbnnaha miayat jaldat 'iidha shfah allh, lmma ghadab ealayha min 'amr yasir 'athna' mrdh, wakanat aimra'at salht, frhmha allah wrhmh bhdhh alftwa. 'iinaa wajadna 'ayuwb sabrana ealaa albla', niem aleabd hw, 'iinah rjjae 'iilaa taeat allh"
  38,45,"wadhkr -ayha alrswl- eibadina wanbya'na: 'iibrahim wa'iishaq wyeqwb; fa'iinahum 'ashab quatan fi taeat allh, wbsyrt fi dynh"
  38,46,"'ina khssnahm bkhast ezymt, hayth jaealna dhikraa aldaar alakhirat fi qlwbhm, femlu laha btaetna, wdeu alnaas 'ilyha, wdhkkarwhm bha. wa'iinahum eindana lamin aladhin akhtarnahum ltaetna, wastfynahm lrsaltna"
  38,47,"'ina khssnahm bkhast ezymt, hayth jaealna dhikraa aldaar alakhirat fi qlwbhm, femlu laha btaetna, wdeu alnaas 'ilyha, wdhkkarwhm bha. wa'iinahum eindana lamin aladhin akhtarnahum ltaetna, wastfynahm lrsaltna"
  38,48,"wadhkur -ayha alrswl- ebadna: 'ismaeyl, walyse, wadha alkfl, bi'ahsan aldhkr; 'iina kla minhum min al'akhyar aladhin akhtarhm allah min alkhlq, wakhtar lahum 'akmal al'ahwal walsfat"
  38,49,"hdha alquran dhikr wshrf lak -ayha alrswl- wlqwmk. wa'iin li'ahl taqwaa allah wtaeth lahsn masir eindana fi janaat 'iqamt, mfttaht lahum abwabha, mutakiiyn fiha ealaa al'arayik almzyanat, yatlubun maa yashtahun min 'anwae alfwakh alkathirat walshrab, min kuli ma tashtahih nfwshm, wtldhh aeynhm"
  38,50,"hdha alquran dhikr wshrf lak -ayha alrswl- wlqwmk. wa'iin li'ahl taqwaa allah wtaeth lahsn masir eindana fi janaat 'iqamt, mfttaht lahum abwabha, mutakiiyn fiha ealaa al'arayik almzyanat, yatlubun maa yashtahun min 'anwae alfwakh alkathirat walshrab, min kuli ma tashtahih nfwshm, wtldhh aeynhm"
  38,51,"hdha alquran dhikr wshrf lak -ayha alrswl- wlqwmk. wa'iin li'ahl taqwaa allah wtaeth lahsn masir eindana fi janaat 'iqamt, mfttaht lahum abwabha, mutakiiyn fiha ealaa al'arayik almzyanat, yatlubun maa yashtahun min 'anwae alfwakh alkathirat walshrab, min kuli ma tashtahih nfwshm, wtldhh aeynhm"